	<h4>Coding patterns</h4>
	<p>A real hacker doesn't doodle, he codes the patterns the table should draw. That's we we provide a whole zen like IDE (aka a textarea) for writing Javascript containing <code>Home</code>,<code>LineTo</code> and <code>MoveTo</code> commands. Variables for <code>min.x, min.y, max.x, max.y and center.x, center.y</code> are also available. Check it out.
	</p>
